Employee Benefits Policy 2024  
 
Health Insurance:  
All full -time employees are eligible for health insurance  
from day one of employment. The company covers 80% of  
premium costs for individual coverage and 60% for family  
coverage. Dental and vision plans a re available as add -ons.  
 
Remote Work Policy:  
Employees may work remotely up to 3 days per week with  
manager approval. A reliable internet connection of at  
least 25 Mbps is required. Remote work equipment including  
laptop and monitor will be provided by  the company.  
 
Training and Development:  
Each employee receives an annual training budget of $2000.  
This can be used for online courses, conferences,  
certifications, or books. Requests must be submitted  
through the HR portal at least 2 weeks in advance.  
 
Performance Reviews:  
Performance reviews are conducted twice yearly in June  
and December. Employees are rated on a scale of 1 to 5  
across four dimensions: technical skills, collaboration,  
delivery, and innovation. Ratings directly influence  
annual sa lary adjustments.